heroes.name: Love
heroes.desc: A warm, embracing presence that reminds you you’re not alone. This master appears when you open your heart, to forgive, to reconnect, and to love yourself and others from a higher, kinder place.

heroes.name: Willpower
heroes.desc: A heroic force that pushes you to keep going when motivation fades. This master appears when you choose action over excuses and reminds you that discipline is love in movement.

heroes.name: Light
heroes.desc: The one who illuminates your path when confusion or fear tries to cover it. This master appears when you ask for clarity and helps you see possibilities, solutions, and the next right step.

heroes.name: Consciousness
heroes.desc: A guide who helps you wake up to what is really happening inside you. This master appears when you decide to act with spiritual intention, to see your patterns, and to choose from awareness instead of impulse.

heroes.name: Balance
heroes.desc: The guardian of harmony between body, mind, emotion, and spirit. This master appears when you are about to go to an extreme and reminds you to stay centered, grounded, and in rhythm with life.
